{"tid":772060,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［好人好事］ 原來香港地仲有好人架","createTime":"2018-08-08T12:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T13:13:55.000Z","uid":5038,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b44d5795e8aa1fb594d1e24157329c04f496c22","tid":772060,"uid":5038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的 早幾日坐紅van 唔見左個散紙包<br />\n入面錢唔算多 得百幾 同埋張有自動增值八達通<br />\n同d濕星野<br />\n<br />\n今日個小巴司機可應搵到我有個電話 打斜我 同我講銀包係佢度<br />\n我一拎個陣 發現d野 錢銀都係曬度<br />\n呢下已經覺得香港地仲有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n失而復得係勁開心<br />\n係呢個咁冷漠社會入面 竟然仲有呢d好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次又係唔見野 由行出鋪頭到番去再搵幾分鐘時間 都話冇 叫佢俾cctv我睇 我去搵番個人出黎都唔俾<br />\n個陣仲要係年三十 搞到冇身份證同卡過左個農歷年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再次多謝個小巴司機 祝佢好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b443a733c8e6d03d59104ac707f99f1914a687d","tid":772060,"uid":13694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"唉，今日喺中環跌左3500，轉個頭返去行翻原路已經無左"},{"pid":"9b1fc04b3ccf137a182bff93a7d33d92ea15f448","tid":772060,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"住觀塘？"},{"pid":"42a1d8ce56e78db2f12d4ee9c779bf1256b8d1c4","tid":772060,"uid":5038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b443a733c8e6d03d59104ac707f99f1914a687d","tid":772060,"uid":13694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"唉，今日喺中環跌左3500，轉個頭返去行翻原路已經無左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"唔話好3500 35跌咗都會俾人執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkg